              <a href="#" class="card-link">Read More</a>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="service-card">
            <img src="/assets/Homeloan.jpg" alt="Personal Loan" class="card-image" />
            <div class="card-content">
              <span class="card-tag">Personal Loan</span>
              <h2 class="card-title">On-the-Spot Personal Loans</h2>
              <p class="card-description">Get your personal loan of 100k with
                0% interest rate and within no time</p>
              <a href="#" class="card-link">Read More</a>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="service-card">
            <img src="..\assets\Homeloan.jpg" alt="Education Loan" class="card-image" />
            <div class="card-content">
              <span class="card-tag">Education Loan</span>
              <h2 class="card-title">Fund Your Education</h2>
              <p class="card-description">The Education Loan makes it easy for
                you and achieve your life goals</p>
              <a href="#" class="card-link">Read More</a>
